## Detailed Analysis

### 1. American Express Blue Cash Everyday - Best Overall for Groceries

**Key specs:**
- Sign-up bonus: $200 after $2,000 spend in 6 months
- Rewards rate: 3% at US supermarkets (up to $6K/year), 3% on gas, 3% on online retail, 1% on everything else
- Annual fee: $0
- APR: 19.24%-29.99% variable

**Why it wins:**

No annual fee and 3% back at US supermarkets up to $6,000/year. The math: $500/month in groceries × 3% = $15/month = $180/year, completely free. If your grocery bill stays under $6K/year, this gives you the best value without paying for rewards you won't fully use. The $200 sign-up bonus after $2,000 spend is basically a free month of groceries.

**Real-world scenario:** Spending $500/month on groceries

- Monthly rewards: $15.00
- Annual rewards: $180.00
- Annual fee: $0
- **Net annual value: $180.00**

